text.section:
All proposed personal service contracts, tax incentive agreements, and memoranda of agreement received by the Legislative Research Commission shall be submitted to the committee to:
Examine the stated need for the service or benefit to the Commonwealth of the motion picture or entertainment production;
Examine whether the service could or should be performed by state personnel, for personal service contracts and memoranda of agreement;
Examine the amount and duration of the contract or agreement; and
Examine the appropriateness of any exchange of resources or responsibilities.
